        <section>
            <h2>What is Anime?</h2>
            <p>Anime is a style of animated storytelling that began in Japan. It features colorful characters, exciting plots, and deep emotions. Anime is popular all over the world among kids, teens, and even adults. There are many anime genres like action, fantasy, romance, and sci-fi. Some famous anime include Naruto, Beyblade, Pokémon, and Dragon Ball Z.</p>
        </section>

